keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
" map g scrollToTop
map <space>j previousTab
map <space>k nextTab
map h goBack
map H scrollLeft
map l goForward
map L scrollRight
map i focusInput
unmap g0
unmap g$
map 0 firstTab
map $ lastTab
map [ goPrevious
map ] goNext
